/* 
Sure! Here's the **detailed breakdown part-by-part**, like **Part 4: Address Section** and what‚Äôs inside each part:

---

### üîπ **Part 1: Global Styles & Variables**

Includes:

* `:root` ‚Äî CSS variables like `--primary-purple`, `--text-light`, `--bg-dark-transparent`
* Base font settings, global background, and padding
* `.checkout-page-background` ‚Äî background image, font, and top-level layout styling

---

### üîπ **Part 2: Layout Containers**

Includes:

* `.checkout-container` ‚Äî Flex layout for the entire checkout structure
* `.checkout-main-content` ‚Äî central glass-effect panel
* `.checkout-sidebar` ‚Äî sidebar beside main content

---

### üîπ **Part 3: Order Summary Section**

Includes:

* `.order-summary-container` and `.summary-card` ‚Äî glass card for order details
* `.summary-title` ‚Äî section headings
* `.summary-row`, `.summary-row.savings` ‚Äî line items
* `.summary-total` ‚Äî final amount row
* `.secure-info-box`, `.shield-icon`, `.terms-text`, `a` ‚Äî secure payment message

---

### üîπ **Part 4: Address Section**

Includes:

* `.step-title` ‚Äî ‚ÄúChoose Address‚Äù heading
* `.address-list` ‚Äî list of saved addresses
* `.address-card` ‚Äî glassy clickable card for each address
* `.address-card:before`, `.address-card.selected:after` ‚Äî custom radio button styles
* `.address-card.selected` ‚Äî glow effect on selected card
* `.address-card-content` ‚Äî spacing and layout inside the card
* `.address-header`, `.address-type-badge`, `p` ‚Äî label like ‚ÄúHome‚Äù, address text
* `.address-actions`, `.icon-btn` ‚Äî edit/delete buttons

---

### üîπ **Part 5: Address Form**

Includes:

* `.address-form-container` ‚Äî full container for adding address
* `.form-group`, `.form-row`, `.form-actions` ‚Äî input group layout
* `label`, `input[type="text"]`, `input[type="tel"]`
* `.btn-secondary` ‚Äî cancel/save buttons

---

### üîπ **Part 6: UPI Form Glass Box**

Includes:

* `.upi-form` ‚Äî full UPI box with glass background
* `.form-header`, `.form-header-icon`, `.form-header-title` ‚Äî UPI title row
* `.upi-apps`, `.upi-app-btn`, `.upi-app-btn:hover` ‚Äî GPay/PhonePe/PAYTM etc. icons

---

### üîπ **Part 7: UPI Input Field**

Includes:

* `.form-group` ‚Äî input group container
* `label` ‚Äî "Enter UPI ID"
* `.upi-input-wrapper` ‚Äî input container with inline icon
* `.upi-input-wrapper.error` ‚Äî red border if invalid
* `.upi-status-icon`, `.verified`, `.error` ‚Äî success/error icons
* `.error-message` ‚Äî red error text

---

### üîπ **Part 8: Spinner Styles**

Includes:

* `.spinner`, `.spinner-inline` ‚Äî circular loading animation
* `@keyframes spin` ‚Äî keyframe for spinner rotation

---

### üîπ **Part 9: Buttons**

Includes:

* `.btn-primary`, `.btn-primary:hover` ‚Äî standard buttons
* `.btn-primary.purple-gradient`, `:hover`, `:disabled` ‚Äî purple gradient
* `.payment-btn`, `.payment-btn:disabled`, `.payment-btn:hover`
* `.step-navigation` ‚Äî positions "Next" button to the right

---

### üîπ **Part 10: Save UPI Checkbox**

Includes:

* `.save-details` ‚Äî container for checkbox and label
* `input[type="checkbox"]` ‚Äî hidden browser checkbox
* `::after` ‚Äî custom white tick mark

---

### üîπ **Part 11: Payment Method Layout**

Includes:

* `.payment-layout` ‚Äî two-column Flexbox layout
* `.payment-methods-sidebar` ‚Äî vertical list of buttons (UPI, Card, NetBanking)
* `.method-btn`, `.method-btn.active`, `.method-btn:hover`
* `.method-btn-group` ‚Äî logo and label in each button

---

### üîπ **Part 12: Payment Content Area**

Includes:

* `.payment-content` ‚Äî main form area on right
* `.payment-form` ‚Äî form container
* `.form-group`, `.form-row`, input and label styles reused here

---

### üîπ **Part 13: NetBanking Dropdown**

Includes:

* `.custom-dropdown`, `.dropdown-header` ‚Äî dropdown structure
* `.dropdown-list`, `li`, `li:hover`, `li.selected` ‚Äî items inside dropdown
* `.bank-logo`, `.bank-logo-small` ‚Äî payment provider logos
* `.radio-icon`, `.radio-icon::after` ‚Äî selection circle

---


